To compile and install

Ultra Quick Version:

% tar -zxf bali-phy-<version>.tgz
% cd bali-phy-<version>
% ./configure
% make
% make install

Quick Version:

1. Extract the sources:

% tar -zxf bali-phy-<version>.tgz

2. Make a build directory

% mkdir bali-phy-build
% cd bali-phy-build

3. Run the configure script in the bali-phy directory:

% ../bali-phy-<version>/configure

By default, the software will be installed in /usr/local

If you wish to install it somewhere else, say $HOME/local
then run:

% ../bali-phy-<version>/configure --prefix=$HOME/local

4. Build the software

% make

5. Install the software

% make install

This will install the software in the directory <prefix>/bin/.